node.text:
We were fortunate enough to spend a weekend in Yokosuka, Japan entertaining the families living on the base there. We would like to thank the staff of the HMS Albion for their wonderful tour. 
Featuring Dakota Roche, Gary Young, Matthias Dandois, Josh Borden and Omar Hassan.

Video: Colin Mackay

node.text: You know those giant bowls you often see at parks that just don’t get much attention? Well, that’s the main attraction for @KrisFoxBMX and the @FastAndLooseBMX crew who live for the deep end! This one is @ClairemontSkatepark, clip: @GarybYoung

node.text: It’s a crazy feeling when these two are together. For all they have done in BMX.  @DakRoche @DennisEnarson 🏁 @JeffZPhoto

node.text: It didn’t take @TheMajorBMX much convincing to join us in Richmond for the Vans x @RADShare project. Aimed at uplifting local underserved communities and empowering more kids to ride BMX, RADShare is making BMX more accessible through efforts to close the opportunity gap. See the video on youtube/vans Photos: @ColinMackayBMX
